<!-- 계약체결 실무흐름도 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-500">account_tree</span>
      계약체결 실무흐름도
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1">낙찰통지 → 서류 징구 → 계약서 작성 → 보증금 납부 → 계약 체결</p>
  </div>

  <div class="p-6">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">flag</span>
          PHASE 1 — 계약 준비
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-blue-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">낙찰통지 · 사전 확인</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 낙찰자에게 <strong class="text-blue-700">낙찰통지서</strong> 발송</li>
            <li>• 낙찰자 자격 확인 (사업자등록, 면허, 부정당업자 제재 여부)</li>
            <li>• 예산 배정 및 집행 가능 여부 확인</li>
            <li class="text-xs text-red-600">※ 낙찰통지 후 10일 이내 계약 체결 의무</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-violet-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-violet-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-violet-800 mb-2">서류 징구</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">사업자등록증</strong> 사본 (법인인감 날인)</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">인감증명서</strong> (3개월 이내 발급분)</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-violet-700">청렴서약서</strong> (모든 계약 필수)</li>
            <li>• 산출내역서, 공정예정표 (공사·용역 해당 시)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">flag</span>
          PHASE 2 — 계약서 작성 · 체결
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-amber-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-amber-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">계약보증금 납부 · 면제 확인</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 계약금액의 <strong class="text-amber-700">10% 이상</strong> 납부 확인 (시행령 제37조)</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-amber-700">면제 대상:</strong> 물품·용역 5천만원 이하, 공사 1억원 이하</li>
            <li>• 납부 방법: 현금/보증보험증권/은행 지급보증서/공제조합 보증서</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-orange-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-800 mb-2">계약서 작성 · 날인</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• <strong class="text-orange-700">필수 기재:</strong> 계약 목적, 금액, 이행기간, 보증금, 지체상금</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-orange-700">대면:</strong> 법인인감·직인 날인 (2부 작성)</li>
            <li>• <strong class="text-orange-700">전자계약:</strong> 나라장터 전자서명 (2천만원 초과 의무)</li>
            <li class="text-xs text-slate-500">※ 5천만원(물품·용역) / 1억원(공사) 이하: 계약서 생략 가능</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-300 text-2xl">arrow_downward</span></div>

      <div class="mb-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:14px">flag</span>
          PHASE 3 — 결재 · 교부
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-green-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">결재 · 계약서 교부</h4>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1">
            <li>• 내부 결재 완료 → 계약서 <strong class="text-green-700">교부</strong></li>
            <li>• 발주기관·계약상대자 각 1부 보관</li>
            <li>• 전자계약 시 나라장터 시스템에 원본 보관</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <details open class="mt-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      <summary class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-slate-500">info</span>
        <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700">참고 안내</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 ml-auto">생략 기준 · 감사대비</span>
      </summary>
      <div class="p-4 space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500">check_circle</span>
            <div class="w-full">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">계약서 작성 생략 기준 <span class="text-xs font-normal bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">시행령 제50조</span></h4>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-400">inventory_2</span>
                  <div><span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">물품·용역</span><p class="text-green-700 font-bold">5천만원 이하</p></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-400">construction</span>
                  <div><span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">공사</span><p class="text-green-700 font-bold">1억원 이하</p></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-500 mt-2">※ 생략해도 청구서·납품서·견적서 등 증빙 보관 필수</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-500">gavel</span>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">감사 대비 체크리스트</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>청렴서약서 누락</strong> — 가장 흔한 지적, 모든 계약에서 필수</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>인감증명서 유효기간 초과</strong> — 3개월 초과 서류 징구 시 부적정</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>계약서 생략 남용</strong> — 5천만원 초과인데 미작성 시 위반</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-400 text-lg mt-0.5">warning</span><span><strong>사후 계약변경</strong> — 변경공사 완료 후 변경계약 시 감사 지적</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</div>
